"{\"uid\": \"hellomagazine.com-fashion-royal-style-709404-princess-charlene-monaco-fitted-jumpsuit-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Princess Charleneproved that she has the designer wardrobe of dreams once again as she stepped out in a form-fitting jumpsuit and a must-see handbag for the Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 157, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.5661431352722935, \"rank\": 0.7288500336048437, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Monagasque royal attended the Heads of State reception at Elysse Palace before arriving at the opening ceremony with her husbandPrince Albert II.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Princess Charlene, 46, looked stylish in the white bespoke Louis Vuitton jumpsuit that cinched at the waist, paired with silver metallic heels from royal-favourite brand Gianvito Rossi.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene,_Princess_of_Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9999992690571105, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Princess Charlene\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene,_Princess_of_Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene,_Princess_of_Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0156925082306557e-25, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}, {\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentino_Rossi\", \"score\": 0.9412600813204611, \"rank\": 0.05753681251658636, \"text\": \"Rossi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentino_Rossi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valentino_Rossi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mother-of-two held a Louis Vuitton 'Capucines Silver Holographic Aligator Leather' handbag, and the designer buy is worth over \\u00a326k/\\u20ac31k.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0156925082306557e-25, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for her hair, the royal opted for a blow-out style with bangs that perfectly framed her face, while Charlene's makeup looked flawless as she sported a touch of grey eyeshadow, fluttering false lashes, a rosy blush, and nude lipstick.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.999997550535953, \"rank\": 2.4494701501434577e-06, \"text\": \"Charlene\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlene_Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prince Albert, 66, coordinated with his wife perfectly as he looked smart for the occasion in a red suit jacket, a pair of white trousers, and a grey and red striped tie.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"score\": 0.9975875803566208, \"rank\": 0.00230015848071635, \"text\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The royal couple did not let the rain spoil the ceremony, and the pair were pictured smiling from the sidelines wearing ponchos with their two children, nine-year-old twins Prince Jacques and Princess Gabriella.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier that day, the Monaco royals were hosted by the President of the French Republic Mister.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6909524938395442e-15, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emmanuel Macron and his wife Brigitte Marie-Claude Macron for a Heads of State reception at the Palace of Elysee.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.076561152627817e-15, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"senten